{"tid":2233004,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–為何有時候落鹽到甜味食物後反而會覺得更甜","createTime":"2020-10-06T21:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T08:25:32.000Z","uid":38861,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0feb61f988c20e14b9056d69360285d4f3848108","tid":2233004,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T21:44:58.000Z","msg":"你有無曾經試過，加少少鹽到甜味的食物之後，感覺反而會更加甜?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WbkOaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WbkOaf.jpg&h=6aede898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟是心理作用，還是有確實的機制存在呢？<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）早前曾經深入淺出舌頭的甜味感測機制，可到這裡溫故知新：<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/474464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F474464&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=48d7c80f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/474464</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTnwaoY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTnwaoY.jpg&h=097e1c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單來說，甜味物質與味蕾上的T1R2及T1R3合併，其後觸發一系列的反應，最終導致電流經由神經細胞傳到大腦，再由大腦分析電流訊息，製造甜味的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）除T1R之外，舌頭上亦有名為SGLT1的蛋白質。<br />\n當有葡萄糖及鈉離子（從NaCl食用鹽得來）同時存在的話，SGLT1便會把葡萄糖及鈉離子同時收入細胞之內，觸發感測甜味的機制。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCg5eQH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCg5eQH.jpg&h=4715f922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這SGLT1蛋白質只會對葡萄糖及鈉離子產生反應，換言之，代糖以及鉀鹽便不會觸發這一套機制。<br />\n<br />\n我們舌頭上相信有三種感測甜味的細胞，只擁有T1R、只擁有SGLT1以及同時擁有T1R和SGLT1。<br />\n<br />\n鈉離子與葡萄糖的存在，將會在T1R的前提下額外觸發SGLT1的機制，因此我們主觀上會感覺到甜味的感覺更為強烈。<br />\n<br />\n當然，若然食用鹽（NaCl)添加過量的話，鹹味最終會蓋過所增進的甜味效益。<br />\n而如何拿掐箇中的平衡，那就要取決於廚師的功力和經驗了。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"red\">like</span>以及<span class=\"green\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=721adf66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=361e9e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcell%2Ffulltext%2FS0092-8674&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=8f927e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674</a>(03)00844-4?_returnURL=https%3A%2F%<a href=\"http://2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=663563cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">2Flinkinghub.elsevier.com</a>%2Fretrieve%2Fpii%2FS0092867403008444%3Fshowall%3Dtrue<br />\n<br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/epdf/10.1111/apha.13529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fepdf%2F10.1111%2Fapha.13529&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=c501cd41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/epdf/10.1111/apha.13529</a>"},{"pid":"fc88a1ed78cff5ef3f5ffd3d221b48d1e8f00387","tid":2233004,"uid":124603,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T21:47:18.000Z","msg":"唔怪得啲人焗曲奇餅會最後灑少少鹽係面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3a42b116a6298219ac9dffde422a9731ee642f","tid":2233004,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc88a1ed78cff5ef3f5ffd3d221b48d1e8f00387","tid":2233004,"uid":124603,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T21:47:18.000Z","msg":"唔怪得啲人焗曲奇餅會最後灑少少鹽係面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T21:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來有咁的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf10e0a31caf50ee3d5b3983dd654eb80eed188","tid":2233004,"uid":18605,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:21:51.000Z","msg":"用代糖來煮餸得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92027d5657211ce8b74a8271210a04483a0f28e","tid":2233004,"uid":93385,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:22:32.000Z","msg":"咁有時整鹹嘅嘢食話再落少少糖令佢唔好係死鹹呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277f31735efa332b35ea33f88617958641c71b0f","tid":2233004,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:26:05.000Z","msg":"菠蘿"},{"pid":"4b7a16db2b9b92197b64ee9dea3b7e05f8b8e58f","tid":2233004,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T22:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed22f47e8dcfce2b9f6ca3b96ef6c89688e568a","tid":2233004,"uid":46576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-